<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <title>Compository | Compare GitHub Repositories with ease !</title>

    <% include ../partials/head %>
  </head>
  <body>

    <% include ../partials/header %>

    <section class="container-fluid">

      <!-- Landing page cover -->
      <section class="row text-center display-height landing-page-cover page-cover">
        <article>
          <h1>Compository</h1>
          <h2>The tool to compare the activity of GitHub repositories.</h2>
        </article>
        <article class="call-to-action">
          <button type="button" data-scroll-target="compare" class="scroll-action btn btn-primary btn-lg">Start Comparing !</button>
          <button type="button" data-scroll-target="about" class="scroll-action btn btn-secondary btn-lg">What's the point ?</button>
        </article>
      </section>

      <% include ../partials/repository_selection %>

      <!-- About & Purpose section -->
      <section id="about" class="row pattern-bg-light  padding-md text-center">
        <article class="col-xs-10 col-xs-offset-1 col-sm-10 col-sm-offset-1 col-md-10 col-md-offset-1 white-bg padding-sm box-shadow text-justify">
          <h1 class="text-center">What's the point ?</h1>
          <hr />
          <section class="row">
            <article class="col-xs-10 col-xs-offset-1 col-sm-10 col-sm-offset-1">
              <p>
                Compository is a web application that allows users to compare GitHub repositories.
              </p>
              <p>
                If you hesitate between several different librairies to use in your projects,
                Compository will help you make a choice by showing you which GitHub repositories
                are the more active, and by comparing side by side their statistics.
                It will also help you exclude dead software from your options.
              </p>
              <article class="text-center">
                <button type="button" data-scroll-target="compare" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg margin-sm scroll-action">Start Comparing !</button>
              </article>
            </article>
          </section>
        </article>
      </section>

    </section>

    <% include ../partials/footer %>
  </body>
</html>
